 applications and expanding its functionality. Check out </SPAN><A href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-copilot/microsoft-copilot-for-finance" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><SPAN data-contrast="none">this site</SPAN></A><SPAN data-contrast="auto"> for more information.</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:279}">&nbsp;</SPAN></LI> </UL></description>
