ot in Excel to create a new column with time zones.</span></span></LI> <LI><STRONG>Thursday, 5-Sep</STRONG>&nbsp;– <A href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/excel/converting-text-to-numbers-using-copilot-for-excel/m-p/4237585#M237677" target="_blank">Converting Text to Numbers using Copilot for Excel</A><BR /><BR /><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Work with Copilot in Excel to prompt it to give better results." style="width: 400px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/617024i2FA6F426A367E1E0/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;px=400" role="button" title="GrahmSchneider13_0-1725479361071.png" alt="Work with Copilot in Excel to prompt it to give better results." /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Work with Copilot in Excel to prompt it to give better results.</span></span></LI> <LI><STRONG>Friday, 6-Sep</STRONG>&nbsp;–&nbsp;<A href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/excel/using-copilot-in-excel-to-convert-survey-responses-into-an/m-p/4238599#M237772" target="_blank">Using&nbsp;<SPAN>Copilot in Excel to convert survey responses into an overall score</SPAN></A><BR /><BR /><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Use Copilot in Excel to calculate a running total from survey results within the table." style="width: 624px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/617025i14BE1945CAAA9A55/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="GrahmSchneider13_1-1725479441144.png" alt="Use Copilot in Excel to calculate a running total from survey results within the table." /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Use Copilot in Excel to calculate a running total from survey results within the table.</span></span> <P>&nbsp;</P> </LI> </UL> <P><SPAN>These posts are pinned within the&nbsp;<A href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/excel/bd