<title>Modernized Excel Grid (part 2)</title>
<link>https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/excel-blog/modernized-excel-grid-part-2/ba-p/4176475</link>
<description><P><SPAN>Dive into the latest enhancements for Excel for the web, where we've streamlined your spreadsheet experience to be more intuitive and efficient. Now, previewing hyperlinks, customizing your view, renaming sheets, and more, is smoother than ever, allowing you to focus on what matters most—your data.<BR /></SPAN></P> <P><SPAN data-contrast="none"><BR /><STRONG>Hyperlink Previews</STRONG></SPAN><STRONG>&nbsp;</STRONG></P> <P><SPAN data-contrast="none">Now, when you hover over web or internal links, you'll see improved hyperlink previews with options to copy, edit, or remove the link. If a thumbnail of the linked page is available, you'll see that too, giving you a better idea of where the link will take you.</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}">&nbsp;<BR /><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Hyperlink previews" style="width: 944px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/598319iDAD02604D6D47D53/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="Hyperlink cards.gif" alt="Hyperlink previews" /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Hyperlink previews</span></span></SPAN></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <P><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <H3 aria-level="2" id="toc-hId--544259241"><STRONG>Easily Adjust Zoom in Status Bar&nbsp;</STRONG></H3> <P><SPAN data-contrast="auto">Customizing your grid zoom just got easier with the status bar. You can now quickly edit zoom values to suit your preferences.</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:2,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:330}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Easily adjust the zoom in the status bar" style="width: 899px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/599414iFE036B3B4AFEFE2F/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="ZoomComboBox.gif" alt="Easily adjust the zoom in the status bar" /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Easily adjust the zoom in the status bar</span></span></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <H3 aria-level="2" id="toc-hId-1943253592"><STRONG>Hassle-free Sheet Rename&nbsp;</STRONG></H3> <P><SPAN data-contrast="none">Renaming sheets is now a breeze. Simply go to the sheet tab and double-click to rename it directly—no more navigating through dialogs.</SPAN></P> <P><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="Easily rename sheets" style="width: 900px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/598320i6D38BDB5E753FC7D/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="In-line Sheet Rename.gif" alt="Easily rename sheets" /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Easily rename sheets</span></span></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <H3 aria-level="2" id="toc-hId-135799129"><STRONG>Open Local Files in Your Browser with Excel for the Web&nbsp;</STRONG></H3> <P><SPAN data-contrast="auto">We've added a handy "Open files from this device" option in the file menu. This lets you upload a local file to your OneDrive and access it directly from your browser.</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Open local files from the file menu" style="width: 555px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/600428iB93372A382272400/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="open local files.png" alt="Open local files from the file menu" /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Open local files from the file menu</span></span></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <H3 aria-level="2" id="toc-hId--1671655334"><STRONG>New Keyboard Shortcuts for Faster Access&nbsp;</STRONG></H3> <P><SPAN data-contrast="none">Good news for keyboard shortcut enthusiasts! We've added support for accelerator keyboard shortcuts (Alt, E, Alt, V, Alt, I, Alt, O) and over 120 legacy shortcuts. Additionally, we have modernized the Keyboard Shortcuts dialog, with richer information and styling.</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="New keyboard shortcuts" style="width: 999px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/598322i26FCCD641BBD1AA1/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="keyboard shortcuts.png" alt="New keyboard shortcuts" /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">New keyboard shortcuts</span></span></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <H3 id="toc-hId-815857499"><STRONG>One Click feedback and Help&nbsp;</STRONG></H3> <P><SPAN data-contrast="auto">You can now quickly access shortcuts to Feedback, Help, and Keyboard shortcuts, all at your fingertips, from the Status bar.&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335557856&quot;:16777215,&quot;335559738&quot;:220,&quot;335559739&quot;:220,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="New feedback and help shortcuts on the status bar" style="width: 800px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/601190i778C1856E48EF27A/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="1f3866d7-12a5-42c0-8c93-1553e9d9d1bd.jpg" alt="New feedback and help shortcuts on the status bar" /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">New feedback and help shortcuts on the status bar</span></span></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <H3 id="toc-hId-1495915867" id="toc-hId--991596964"><STRONG>Availability</STRONG></H3> <P>These features are currently rolling out to all Excel for the web users.<BR /><BR />Read up on the other exciting Excel for the web grid enhancements in part one - <A href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/excel-blog/modernized-excel-grid/ba-p/4176473" target="_blank">Modernized Excel Grid</A>.</P> <P><SPAN data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:278}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P></description>
