<title>Celebrating Pride with Excel</title>
<link>https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/excel-blog/celebrating-pride-with-excel/ba-p/4167611</link>
<description><P><SPAN data-contrast="auto">Join us as we celebrate Pride and the spirit of radical joy! “Radical joy” is an anthem to those who thrive against all odds. The joy that radiates and inspires. The joy that is not dependent on outside forces but is within us and within our control, and when expressed, can help make change for all and inspire others to do the same. </SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><SPAN data-contrast="auto">Discover everything Pride at </SPAN><A href="https://unlocked.microsoft.com/pride/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><SPAN data-contrast="none">unlocked.microsoft.com/pride</SPAN></A><SPAN data-contrast="auto">.</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <P><SPAN data-contrast="auto"><STRONG>Take action:</STRONG></SPAN><STRONG>&nbsp;</STRONG></P> <P><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P> <UL> <LI data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Aptos Narrow" data-listid="1" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><SPAN data-contrast="auto">Embrace the </SPAN><A href="https://unlocked.microsoft.com/pride" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><SPAN data-contrast="none">Stories of joy</SPAN></A><SPAN data-contrast="auto"> and explore them in this <A href="https://1drv.ms/x/s!AovFHtldb3vghDvQSsOY5EUrcBSy?e=lmmDgu" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer">Excel template</A></SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></LI> </UL> <P style=" padding-left : 60px; "><IFRAME src="https://onedrive.live.com/embed?resid=E07B6F5DD91EC58B%21571&amp;authkey=%21AHxDhpQ5JQGV8Yo&amp;em=2&amp;wdAllowInteractivity=False&amp;wdHideGridlines=True&amp;wdHideHeaders=True&amp;wdDownloadButton=True&amp;wdInConfigurator=True&amp;wdInConfigurator=True" width="904" height="519" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></IFRAME></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <UL> <LI data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Aptos Narrow" data-listid="1" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><SPAN data-contrast="auto"><A href="https://insider.microsoft365.com/en-us/blog/embrace-radical-joy-with-pride-theme-in-microsoft-365-for-mac-and-ios" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer">Show your Pride</A> with this special theme for Mac and iOS</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></LI> </UL> <P><span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Show Your Pride in the Preferences dialog box" style="width: 999px;"><img src="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/592607i8D8BD13EC1798DF5/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;px=999" role="button" title="cuong_0-1718649085474.png" alt="Show Your Pride in the Preferences dialog box" /><span class="lia-inline-image-caption" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Show Your Pride in the Preferences dialog box</span></span></P> <P>&nbsp;</P> <P><SPAN data-contrast="auto">Radical joy is more than just a feeling. It’s an anthem to those who thrive against all odds. An ode to beauty. And a reminder that joy is both universal and individual—and we should unite in spreading it everywhere.</SPAN><SPAN data-ccp-props="{}">&nbsp;</SPAN></P></description>
